Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Salvation Through Faith
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
Faith! Faith! Faith! Once a guru said to his pupil, ‘Râma alone has
become everything.’ When a dog began to eat the pupil’s bread, he said
to it： ‘O Râma, wait a little. I shall butter Your bread.’ Such was
his faith in the words of his guru.
